title: Strategic partnership set to bring ancient civilisation to Seoul Museum by 2027

title: How to include fossil fuel communities in Canada's clean energy transition
description: Fossil fuel-dependent communities in Western Canada sit at the center of Canada's energy decisions. A just and inclusive clean energy transition will depend on how well governments listen to these communities and how fast they deal with the forces working to slow down energy decarbonization.
